<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>添加成功</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 40px 20px;
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        color: #333;
      }

      .success-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #e6f7e6; /* 淡绿色背景 */
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: left;
      }

      .success-title {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .success-message {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }

      .success-message:hover {
        color: #1890ff;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="success-container">
      <h1 class="success-title">:) <%= msg %></h1>
      <p class="success-message">
        1秒后将自动跳转，如果没有跳转，请点击<a href="<%= url %>">这里</a>
      </p>
      <script>
        setTimeout(() => {
          window.location.href = "<%= url %>";
        }, 1000);
      </script>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
